title: Watch Face: Executive Diamond
summary: Experience the luster of diamonds upon a serving of gold.
description: This watch face creates a new standard of excellence.  An beautiful and excellent design is bolstered with an array of diamonds functioning as hour markers.  The dial is encircled with smaller diamonds signifying the seconds of a minute.  This is a premium watch face experience.  The diamonds will glisten with all their lustre as you rotate your wrist.  You may view the video on this page to see this effect for yourself.This watch face tells the time with millisecond accuracy.  Every hand is oriented as such and is positioned as a real watch would be.  Every hand is smooth, including the hour and minute hands.This watch face contains two dials which can be configured to tell the day of the week, date or battery level to your liking.Once downloaded, this watch face can be accessed through Android Wear.This watch face was developed and tested on the Moto 360 and Sony smartwatch 3 and will work on most android smartwatches.
descriptionHTML:
This watch face creates a new standard of excellence. An beautiful and excellent design is bolstered with an array of diamonds functioning as hour markers. The dial is encircled with smaller diamonds signifying the seconds of a minute. This is a premium watch face experience. The diamonds will glisten with all their lustre as you rotate your wrist. You may view the video on this page to see this effect for yourself.

This watch face tells the time with millisecond accuracy. Every hand is oriented as such and is positioned as a real watch would be. Every hand is smooth, including the hour and minute hands.

This watch face contains two dials which can be configured to tell the day of the week, date or battery level to your liking.

Once downloaded, this watch face can be accessed through Android Wear.

This watch face was developed and tested on the Moto 360 and Sony smartwatch 3 and will work on most android smartwatches.
